{
  "texts": [
    "34 have proposed a \"Balanced Gaussian Process Dynamical Model (B-GPDMs)\" to predict human intention through human motion signals.",
    "The developed mechanism effectively minimized the 3-D-based data extracted from the essential joints in the lower dimensional regions.",
    "The developed B-GPDM technique effectively collected the inferring characteristics and also reconstructed the respective validations.",
    "Classical learning techniques offered poor accuracy in predicting the activities of pedestrians.",
    "The developed mechanism employed an ensemble mechanism to accomplish the superior intention detected outcomes.Petković et al."
  ]
}